All they need is a guitar, a keyboard and their laptop to create music that goes straight to your body and makes you wanna dance. 

twocolors is the Berlin based act of Pierro and Emil. Their unique strength is a symbiosis of driving electro and melodic pop. The two musicians met at a party in Berlin in September 2015 and soon started writing, producing and distributing their own music independently together. This makes them standalone in the genre. 

With the help of their first fans all over the globe and the YouTube Channels of MrSuicideSheep and MrRevillz the single Follow You (feat. Muringa) gained nearly 11M streams on Spotify and 3,4M views on YouTube. It was also featured on various compilations such as the Tomorrowland Elixier of Live 2016. 

In 2018 new songs are going to be released internationally beginning with the first single “BOY“ in June.
